Paper: hep-th/9710050

Date: 1997-10-06

Title: On the Structure of Quantum Gauge Theories with External Fields

Authors: S. Falkenberg, B. Geyer (Leipzig University), P. Lavrov (Tomsk State

Ped. University) and P. Moshin (Tomsk State University)Comments: 16 pages, LaTeX

Journal-ref: Int.J.Mod.Phys. A13 (1998) 4077-4090

We consider generating functionals of Green's functions with external fieldsin the framework of BV and BLT quantization schemes for general gauge theories.The corresponding Ward identities are obtained, and the gauge dependence isstudied.